        "subject": "LU-3534 osp: start recovery process in OSP",
        "message": "LU-3534 osp: start recovery process in OSP\n\nStart recovery process in OSP after connection.\n1. Master will retrieve update log from slave MDT and\nredo updates if needed. (by checking transno in update).\n\n2. Master will retrieve local update log and resend\nto the slave.\n\nSigned-off-by: wang di <di.wang@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I63cbdd455af7561b34af82fcf9342cfae02e96bd\n"
      },
